Description: Cylinder seal of black steatite, perforated through the centre, bearing an incised inscription in two rectangular frames. Good condition, although slightly worn.
Curator's comments: Bibliography: P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit III (Wiesbaden, 1964), pl. 110, abb. 580; P. Kaplony, 'Die Inschriften der Ägyptischen Frühzeit II (Wiesbaden, 1964), 1167.
Previous owner: Previous owner/ex-collection: Rev George Denis Nash
